'''Helen Prest-Ajayi''', he nọ yin '''Prest-Davies''' to dayi (he dà Prest, yin jiji to azan fọtọnnukunawetọ Zósun owhè 1959). E basi whẹdọtọ oto Naijilia tọn, whekantọ, yọnnu he yọn whanpẹ hugan to otò Naijilia tọn mẹ dayi po. E whẹn dó Glẹnsitomẹ. E yi wehọmẹ daho ''International School'' to Ibadan whẹpodo yi wehọmẹ alavọ tọn ''Obafemi Awolowo University'' fie e plọnnu gándo osẹ́n go tẹ jẹnukọnna whenue é yi nado whlẹn otẹn yọnnu he yọn whanpẹ hugan tọn.
Whenuena ye na ẹn jẹgbakun yọnnu he yọn whanpẹ hugan to Naijilia godo whenue é dó owhè fọtọnnukunẹnẹ to owhè 1979, Helen nọtena otò Naijilia tọn to yovotomẹ nado whlẹn otẹn yọnnu he yọn whanpẹ hugan tọn aihọn mẹ, enẹgodo sọ zindonukọn to wehọmẹ daho ''King's College'' to London, fie e yi gbedewema ''LLM'' tẹ. E sọ́ wazọn taidi linlinhodọtọ to owhè 1990 lẹ. To alọnu Helen wẹ yin ògán na azọnwhe ''Media Business Company''. Ewọ wẹ oviví na nukunmọ̀nu '' Chief Arthur Prest'' podọ ovi
Tonudọtọ ''chief Micheal Godwin Prest''. E do yọnnuvi atọ̀n (3). E wlealọ hẹ asu etọn tintan ajọwatọ Jimmy Davies to owhè 1988.
